OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774624292
OL,3,CPolice admit 'terrible error' telling
OL,4,Cpartner of Ian Coates how he died
OL,6,FSchool caretaker Mr Coates was killed
OL,7,Fjust over an hour after 19-year-old
OL,8,Fundergraduates Barnaby Webber and
OL,9,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar were fatally
OL,10,Fstabbed by paranoid schizophrenic
OL,11,FCalocane in the early hours of June 13
OL,12,F2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774624292
OL,3,CPolice admit 'terrible error' telling
OL,4,Cpartner of Ian Coates how he died
OL,6,FThe inquiry was shown an email from Pc
OL,7,FIndia Proud, who relayed the
OL,8,Finformation that Mr Coates had died in
OL,9,Fa road traffic collision (RTC) and
OL,10,Fspent time with Ms Newton on the
OL,11,Fmorning of June 13, in which she
OL,12,Fexplained it felt "torturous" not to
OL,13,Fbe able to give her more details about
OL,14,Fhow her partner died.
OL,26,@tD@SOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774624292
OL,3,CPolice admit 'terrible error' telling
OL,4,Cpartner of Ian Coates how he died
OL,6,FShe wrote: "At the initial point when
OL,7,FI arrived (at her home address), I was
OL,8,Funsure whether Mr Coates was a victim
OL,9,Fof a road traffic collision or a
OL,10,Fvictim of one of the stabbings as no
OL,11,Fnames were given on the radio and so I
OL,12,Fbelieved the control room to be
OL,13,Fpassing me the correct information as
OL,14,Fthey believed him to be the victim of
OL,15,Fan RTC."
OL,26,@nD@LOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774624292
OL,3,CPolice admit 'terrible error' telling
OL,4,Cpartner of Ian Coates how he died
OL,6,FShe said she "repeatedly went back to
OL,7,Fthe control room to ask if I could
OL,8,Fgive any further information as it
OL,9,Ffelt a bit torturous not to be able to
OL,10,Fdo so", but the radio was busy that
OL,11,Fmorning and she was waiting for call-
OL,12,Fbacks.
OL,14,FShe added: "I know from experience
OL,15,Fthat when you get a death message, you
OL,16,Fwant all the information possible so
OL,17,Fyou can even slightly start processing
OL,18,Fwhat you have been told."
OL,26,@nD@NOUrD@FO]vD@LOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774624292
OL,3,CPolice admit 'terrible error' telling
OL,4,Cpartner of Ian Coates how he died
OL,6,FAsked by counsel to the inquiry Julian
OL,7,FBlake what had gone wrong, Ms Gould
OL,8,Fsaid it was the first time she had
OL,9,Fseen the email.
OL,11,FShe said: "Quite clearly, there has
OL,12,Fbeen a terrible error and the family
OL,13,Fshould not have been given the wrong
OL,14,Finfo as to Mr Coates' cause of death.
OL,16,F"It's not entirely clear where that
OL,17,Fmiscommunication happened, but to be
OL,18,Fclear, that never should have
OL,19,Fhappened."
OL,26,@sD@KOUxD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774624292
OL,3,CPolice admit 'terrible error' telling
OL,4,Cpartner of Ian Coates how he died
OL,6,FShe added: "I think it's quite clear
OL,7,Fthe officer feels awful about what
OL,8,Fhappened but it doesn't take away the
OL,9,Fimpact it had on Elaine and her family
OL,10,Fand it is important police officers
OL,11,Fare trained to understand the impact
OL,12,Fdeath messages have and it's
OL,13,Fabsolutely crucial we make every
OL,14,Fendeavour to pass the correct
OL,15,Finformation."
OL,17,FMs Gould also said she was
OL,18,F"wholeheartedly sorry" for the delay
OL,19,Fin informing Mr Coates' three sons
OL,20,Fthat their father had died.
OL,26,@nD@LOUwD@MO]zD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774624292
OL,3,CPolice admit 'terrible error' telling
OL,4,Cpartner of Ian Coates how he died
OL,6,FShe said: "I have always been aware of
OL,7,Fthe impact that delay had on them and
OL,8,Ffor that I am wholeheartedly sorry for
OL,9,Fthe impact it had.
OL,11,F"In terms of the delay in them being
OL,12,Ftold... I believe as a result of me
OL,13,Fnot knowing they were the sons of Ian
OL,14,Fand when I was informed he had sons, I
OL,15,Ftasked the liaison officers to find
OL,16,Finformation about them but there was
OL,17,Fstill too long of a delay which I take
OL,18,Fresponsibility for."
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774624292
OL,3,CPolice admit 'terrible error' telling
OL,4,Cpartner of Ian Coates how he died
OL,6,FAsked what she thought had gone wrong,
OL,7,FMs Gould told the inquiry the
OL,8,Fsituation was "frenetic" with 11
OL,9,Factive crime scenes and that it was a
OL,10,Fcombination of everything going on
OL,11,Fthat led to the news of their family
OL,12,Fmembers' deaths not being passed on.
OL,14,FIts as the inquiry also heard today
OL,15,Ffrom those victims who survived the
OL,16,Fattack, and have also been critical of
OL,17,FNottinghamshire Police's response to
OL,18,Fthe incident.
OL,20,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@XO]
